Come on.

103
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,150
Try them on.

104
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,840
Look at this color, isn’t it beautiful?

105
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:57,240
Eldest Sister-in-law.

106
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:57,960
I’ll try it on later.

107
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:59,200
Just try it on.

108
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,770
