Eldest Sister-in-law.

110
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,560
Is it inconvenient because there are too many people around?

111
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:07,920
Alright.

112
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:08,840
I’ll leave it here.

113
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,080
You can try it on later.

114
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:10,610
Let's go.

115
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:23,220
I'll make you some hangover soup.

116
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,760
Be careful.

117
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:31,560
Take this.

118
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,210
This will be useful.

119
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:35,120
Handle that one gently.

120
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:35,810
Alright.

121
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:37,970
Second Young Madam.

122
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,300
What are you doing?

123
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:42,220
Aren’t these all Shaoyang’s things?

124
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:44,560
I’m just helping him move them back to Xizhao’s room.

125
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:45,800
Be careful.

126
00:06:46,159 --> 00:06:46,840
Yes.

127
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,720
I'll help too.

128
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:51,640
Be careful.

129
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:56,800
What should I do?

130
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:59,240
We are not a legitimate couple.

131
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:02,540
Do I really need to consummate with Lu Shaoyang?

132
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,570
Fourth Young Madam.

133
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,960
The Old Madam has summoned you.

134
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:15,400
Got it.

135
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:23,460
Look at this embroidery pattern.

136
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,520
Mother.

137
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:28,400
You want to see me?

138
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,120
Look.

139
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,730
This little garment

140
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:32,570
is so lovely.

141
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,200
What do they mean?

142
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:36,120
Are they asking me to have a child?

143
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,000
No way.

144
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:43,680
Xizhao.

145
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,840
You’ve been here for a while.

146
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:49,780
If Shaoyang still doesn’t want to live with you,

147
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,050
you must let me know.

148
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:51,960
Mother.

149
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:53,760
That’s not true.

150
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:55,600
Shaoyang isn’t unwilling.

151
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,880
Then

152
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:58,360
has he upset you?

153
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:00,160
I’ll go deal with him right now.

154
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:00,760
Mother.

155
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,610
You misunderstand.

156
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:05,600
Shaoyang is very good to me.

157
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,530
Then when are you

158
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:08,680
going to give me

159
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:11,440
a grandchild?

160
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,060
My Lord.

161
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:17,860
It's ready.

162
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,320
This is it.

163
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,320
How do I look?

164
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,360
My Lord. You look handsome.

165
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:40,289
It inspires deep admiration in your humble servant.

166
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:42,240
Not bad with the flattery.

167
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:44,100
But you shouldn’t misuse idioms.

168
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,780
You speak wisely, My Lord.

169
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:05,800
Darling.

170
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,770
Don't come over.

171
00:09:10,560 --> 00:09:11,090
Darling.

172
00:09:11,190 --> 00:09:12,520
I have something to tell you.

173
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:13,780
Then speak from there.

174
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:20,930
Darling.

175
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,320
The bracelet from before was broken.

176
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,850
But I know you treasured it.

177
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:26,960
Though it couldn’t be restored,

178
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:29,160
I made a wind chime from it for you.

179
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,520
I hope it brings you

180
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:34,040
some comfort when you see it.

181
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,440
