182
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,440
before marriage.

183
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:42,000
But we ended up doing things in reverse.

184
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,780
Today, I use it as a substitute

185
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:46,280
for the token I owed you on our wedding day.

186
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:56,160
Shaoyang.

187
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:59,250
Thank you for doing all this for me.

188
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,280
Are you not happy?

189
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:06,720
Are you still upset with me for neglecting you before?

190
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:09,560
You didn’t neglect me.

191
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:11,960
It’s the Old Madam.

192
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:14,130
She wants a grandchild.

193
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:17,220
Don’t you want one?

194
00:10:17,640 --> 00:10:18,640
I know in the past

195
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,800
I was wild and reckless, and I hurt you.

196
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:22,440
I apologize for that today.

197
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:24,650
It’s not your fault.

198
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,360
It's

199
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:29,800
my own problem.

200
00:10:31,270 --> 00:10:32,870
Darling. Why do you say that?

201
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:57,320
Actually,

202
00:10:58,000 --> 00:11:00,060
I’m not the same Liu Xizhao as before.

203
00:11:01,310 --> 00:11:02,200
I know.

204
00:11:02,640 --> 00:11:04,400
Through this time I’ve spent getting to know you,

205
00:11:04,400 --> 00:11:05,000
I'm sure

206
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:07,250
I prefer who you are now.

207
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:12,360
Shaoyang.

208
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,100
You’re wonderful.

209
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,520
It’s just that

210
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:22,090
I don’t know how to face you.

211
00:11:33,640 --> 00:11:34,320
Xizhao!

212
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,520
He’s awake.

213
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:03,400
Mr. Liu.

214
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:04,360
Mr. Liu.

215
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:06,720
Mr. Liu.

216
00:12:07,560 --> 00:12:08,200
Mr. Liu.

217
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:13,400
You're awake.

218
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:28,240
It felt like a dream.

219
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:32,480
Your blood pressure and temperature are normal.

220
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,240
You’re fine.

221
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:38,040
Nice to meet you.

222
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:39,320
I’m your attending physician,

223
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:39,960
Lu Shaoyang.
